Without whose vision, drive and dedication
this woodland would not exist"╦
╚This bench was given by the community in memory of
DR ALAN DODGE 1938 - 2014
Loved and respected for his great contribution to village life
and for telling the rich history of Freshford
April 2017"╧
╠In Loving Memory of
Nicholas Patrick McDonagh
30 March 1965 - 2 March 2021
Missed Every Day

IN MEMORY OF
NANNY MAC
HELEN McDONAGH
1938-2003
